Privacy Policy for Islamic Dashboard Chrome Extension

Last Updated: 04/09/2025

1. Introduction
Islamic Dashboard ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our Chrome extension.

2. Information We Collect
2.1 Location Data
- We collect your geographical coordinates to calculate accurate prayer times
- This data is stored locally on your device
- We do not transmit or store your location data on external servers

2.2 User Preferences
- Theme selection (dark/light mode)
- Selected Quran reciter
- Notification preferences
- Prayer time calculation method
- All preferences are stored locally using Chrome's storage API

3. How We Use Your Information
- To provide accurate prayer times based on your location
- To maintain your preferred settings and preferences
- To deliver prayer time notifications
- To play Quran audio from your selected reciter

4. Data Storage and Security
- All data is stored locally on your device
- We use Chrome's secure storage API
- We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data
- We do not share your data with third parties

5. Your Rights and Choices
- You can disable location access at any time
- You can modify or clear your preferences through the extension's settings
- You can uninstall the extension to remove all stored data

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

7. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Your Contact Information].

8. Data Protection
We comply with applicable data protection laws and regulations. We do not collect sensitive personal information, and all data processing is limited to the extension's core functionality.
